I highly recommend his lecture series called Awakening from the Meaning Crisis,

00:55.760 --> 01:00.160
which covers the history and future of humanity's search for meaning.

01:00.840 --> 01:02.560
This is the Lex Friedman podcast.

01:02.720 --> 01:05.840
