Isn't there a strong case to be made that this death thing is a really damn good,

11:06.320 --> 11:11.280
if not anything, a tool to motivate the behavior of humans?

11:12.000 --> 11:18.320
I'm not saying that the avoidance of death is not significant for human beings, but I'm

