13:03.520 --> 13:11.680
That fear seems to be a source of an intense appreciation of the moment, in part.

13:12.480 --> 13:17.360
That's what the Stoics talked about, to meditate on once mortality.

13:17.360 --> 13:17.600
Sure.

13:17.600 --> 13:26.480
